node.text:
Shot at the historic @waldorfnyc while under full reno, we had the best time creating cover magic for the May issue of @holausa! From the amazing creative team and editorial staff to our celebratory 🥂 upon wrapping, it was certainly a memorable photoshoot 🤗 ⁣
⁣
Thank you Team #HolaUSA!⁣
📷: @cesarbalcazar 
💄: @andrea_tiller 
💇🏼‍♀️: @kenna_hair_ 
👗: @stylist_marcocorral

node.title: BTS of My HOLA! Cover Shoot

node.text:
I rounded up some of the key trends I saw on the runways and showrooms of Milan and Paris this past fashion month.

Brands featured: Albagia, Alberta Ferretti, Alexadre Birman, Andrea Mondin Benedetta Bruzziches, Brunello Cucinelli Casadei, Christian Louboutin, Delvaux, Dior, Elena Ghisellini, Elie Saab,  Ermanno Scervino, Escada Etro, Fendi Fratelli Rossetti Gedebe, Giambattista Valli, Gianvito Rossi, Giuseppe Zanotti, Jimmy Choo, Lacoste Lanvin. Les Petits Jouers, Max Mara, Mr & Mrs Italy, N21, Roger Vivier, Santoni, Sara Battaglia, Stuart Weitzman Tod's, Tommy Hilfiger, Valentino, Versace

node.title: Milan & Paris Fashion Week 2019 Trend Report

node.text:
Earlier this year, I had the pleasure of a private visit to the brand new #LGSIGNATURE showroom to experience their incredible OLED R rollable television 📺 
Yes, you read that correctly: a television that is completely rollable!!!
A first of its kind, the #OLEDR screen not only entirely retracts but features some of the best visuals in the industry, all while looking sleek and chic.
Now I just need to get my hands on one to watch all of my #OPguiltypleasures 😉 #LGSIGNATUREOLEDR #ad
